Multiparametric MRI to improve detection of prostate cancer compared with 
transrectal ultrasound-guided prostate biopsy alone: the PROMIS study.

Brown LC(1), Ahmed HU(2)(3), Faria R(4), El-Shater Bosaily A(2)(3), Gabe R(5), 
